Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,============================================================================================Main
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.73,0:01:01.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,平…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.99,0:01:03.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不妙啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.51,0:01:10.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,确实…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.37,0:01:15.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这就是终焉的开端了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.90,0:03:08.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs27\fad(400,800)}ACT 7  屍亂夜與屍群
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.86,0:03:15.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,确实 正在恶化啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.66,0:03:18.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可恶 太残酷了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.13,0:03:19.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小室
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.84,0:03:20.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,干什么
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.27,0:03:22.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你开了枪之后又想怎么办
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.78,0:03:25.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还用问吗 干掉<丧尸>然后把大家…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.48,0:03:26.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你难道忘记了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.26,0:03:31.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,<丧尸>可是会对声音产生反应的 小室
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.68,0:03:36.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.71,0:03:43.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,生者会看见灯光以及我们的身影后聚集于此
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.78,0:03:48.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当然 我们没有拯救所有活人的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.87,0:03:52.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好好看看 要学会适应
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.71,0:03:58.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个世界已经不是仅靠男子气概就能生存下去的地方了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.78,0:04:07.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我还以为毒岛学姐会有些与别人不同的想法
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.37,0:04:12.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别会错意了 小室
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.01,0:04:16.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我只是在说明现实而已
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.90,0:04:18.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,并非我自己喜欢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.55,0:04:28.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 往外看的时候动作小点哦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.43,0:04:40.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,简直就是地狱
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.32,0:04:51.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸 妈妈呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.13,0:04:59.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等会就能见到妈妈了 来吧 这边
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.67,0:05:05.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜托了 请让我们进去
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.62,0:05:08.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我带着小孩无路可逃
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.40,0:05:16.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜托了 请让我们进去
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.06,0:05:18.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别进来 到别处去
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.08,0:05:23.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜托了 我怎么样无所谓 请让小孩 让我女儿进去…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.58,0:05:34.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.17,0:05:38.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,开门！ 再不开我就破门了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.01,0:05:39.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.71,0:05:42.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要破门了！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.36,0:05:43.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等…等等
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.93,0:05:45.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现…现在就开
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.10,0:05:52.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢 得救…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.38,0:06:14.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,南无阿弥陀佛…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.32,0:06:15.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,饶恕我
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.52,0:06:23.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,饶恕我…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.52,0:06:28.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,饶恕我
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.55,0:06:30.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,饶恕我
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.59,0:06:43.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸 爸爸
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.01,0:06:45.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.20,0:06:51.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸…没事的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.50,0:06:55.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,躲起来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.77,0:06:59.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,千万别让任何人发现
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.00,0:07:03.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,找个地方…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.01,0:07:05.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,躲起来
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.39,0:07:20.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.07,0:07:23.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.51,0:07:27.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.89,0:07:30.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.10,0:07:37.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要跟爸爸一起 永远跟爸爸在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.17,0:07:49.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.00,0:07:59.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Rock&Roll！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.59,0:08:15.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用从没试射过的别人的枪 一下子就爆头了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.69,0:08:18.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然我在这方面真他妹的是个天才啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.10,0:08:19.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘛 虽说距离也不够100米
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.62,0:08:26.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,高城～
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.02,0:08:43.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,平野
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.42,0:08:45.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么事
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.74,0:08:47.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不是不打算行动的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.07,0:08:51.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了活下去 不是要放弃别人的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.48,0:08:53.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那可是只小萝莉啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.64,0:08:56.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,肯定得救她的吧？ 我会在这里掩护你的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.88,0:09:02.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿孝？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.06,0:09:04.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要去救个小孩
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.71,0:09:06.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那…那么我也去
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.05,0:09:09.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 你在大门口守着吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.68,0:09:11.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我会骑机车过去的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.84,0:09:12.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.74,0:09:13.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让他去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.04,0:09:17.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,君子一言
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.86,0:09:20.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉 毒岛…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.86,0:09:21.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 讶子
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.29,0:09:24.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我看来就是这种人呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.13,0:09:27.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我当然知道
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.46,0:09:34.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里无论发生什么我都会守护住的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.83,0:09:36.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你放心去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.99,0:09:38.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿孝
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.94,0:09:42.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,至少把这个带上
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.13,0:09:52.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要太过于信任枪
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.80,0:09:54.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要一开枪<丧尸>就会聚集过来
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.53,0:09:57.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不管怎么说 机车还是会发出声音的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.82,0:10:02.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没错 不过 机车是为了移动才发出声音的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.87,0:10:06.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但枪声响起时 你却并没有移动
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.78,0:10:08.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿孝
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.82,0:10:57.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底吵什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.61,0:10:59.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,发生好事了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.79,0:11:01.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.36,0:11:05.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们明白了自己其实还是人
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.58,0:11:16.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Reload
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.62,0:11:23.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那里吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.39,0:11:40.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好疼…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.15,0:11:43.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的 果然不能像动画一般华丽呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.04,0:11:57.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果真是个天才
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.10,0:12:01.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是自然
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.04,0:12:04.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要 别过来
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.63,0:12:09.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人家…明明什么坏事都没做过
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.48,0:12:11.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妈妈…爸爸…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.62,0:12:15.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.38,0:12:23.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你很坚强呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.12,0:12:25.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再忍耐一会就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.86,0:12:34.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老师 你快起来啦 静香老师
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.52,0:12:41.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦？ 要吃早饭了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.00,0:12:45.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,少发呆了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.96,0:12:47.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 不要～
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.60,0:12:54.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不准欺负小女孩
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.11,0:12:59.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大哥哥 背后
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.75,0:13:11.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢 帮了我大忙
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.23,0:13:15.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,平野
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.48,0:13:17.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,高城
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.24,0:13:25.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,静…静香老师…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.92,0:13:27.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Hi～
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.84,0:13:29.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要做逃走的准备了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.45,0:13:31.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,搞出这么大的骚动
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.31,0:13:32.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还怎么能留在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.26,0:13:35.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也做好随时能离开的准备
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.54,0:13:36.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好…好的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.25,0:13:43.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,宫本
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.50,0:13:46.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那里就交给毒岛学姐 你也过来帮忙
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.31,0:13:52.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,静香老师就不劳烦你了 总之先找点什么穿上吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.19,0:13:54.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 怪不得我觉得那么冷
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.41,0:13:56.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么开始准备车吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.75,0:13:58.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽说现在能够上车
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.22,0:14:01.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为<丧尸>正被小室吸引着
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.76,0:14:06.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他到底想怎么办啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.64,0:14:09.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那样子靠机车也回不来啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.84,0:14:13.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就只能去接他了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.55,0:14:23.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那…那个 老师说什么奇怪的话了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.04,0:14:25.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,毕竟也有车钥匙
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.51,0:14:27.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 是个好主意
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.77,0:14:31.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,话说也只能如此了呢 就这么决定了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.79,0:14:34.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,救出小室后马上逃往河对面
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.96,0:14:36.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了 开始准备吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.57,0:14:41.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.20,0:14:51.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸 死掉了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.06,0:15:00.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大哥哥？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.42,0:15:16.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他是为了保护你而死的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.41,0:15:18.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是个了不起的爸爸
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.33,0:15:35.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.82,0:15:56.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好多啊 能装得下吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.27,0:15:59.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,话说回来该怎么装啊 要是中途<丧尸>来了的话…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.02,0:16:03.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只能像网游里的盗贼一样 偷偷摸摸干了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.67,0:16:05.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么就这样吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.01,0:16:16.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦？ 这啥啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.01,0:16:20.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,方向盘是反的 那…那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.16,0:16:27.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别太大声了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.71,0:16:29.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不然会吸引<丧尸>过来的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.94,0:16:31.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,逃不掉吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.50,0:16:34.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,路上有很多
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.61,0:16:37.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不往路上逃不就好了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.87,0:16:40.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道叫我飞天吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.91,0:16:48.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,装上物品 救出小室跟女孩子后逃脱
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.81,0:16:52.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想法倒不错 不过那数量估计就连Hum-Vee也…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.89,0:16:56.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想救出他们不动用坦克什么的估计是没搞头了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.62,0:17:07.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,或者是小室能想出什么办法逃出来…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.23,0:17:11.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原来如此！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.86,0:17:18.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,厉害啊 小室
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.73,0:17:25.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别看地上 看着围墙走
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.67,0:17:30.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看着围墙走 看着围墙…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.27,0:17:33.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别…别这…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.92,0:17:34.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.09,0:17:38.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.36,0:17:40.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不害怕吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.50,0:17:42.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,害怕 大哥哥呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.76,0:17:43.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不怕
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.00,0:17:46.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才怪…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.43,0:17:48.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,平野呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.59,0:17:50.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唉？ 应该还在二楼吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.97,0:17:51.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.76,0:17:53.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真不知道他到底是厉害还是迟钝
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.52,0:17:56.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呃？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.19,0:18:02.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个…各位怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.05,0:18:05.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你好像很乐在其中呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.33,0:18:08.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟小室比起来根本不值一提
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.80,0:18:12.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那…那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.13,0:18:14.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你再说一次
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.90,0:18:15.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,尿尿
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.10,0:18:19.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能忍吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.45,0:18:21.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个…不行
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.07,0:18:25.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仅仅一天世界便遭毁灭 跟莫名其妙的家伙战斗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.96,0:18:29.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs26}再加上做些像英雄一般的行为最终导致这步田地…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.82,0:18:32.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs26}我已经受不了了…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.64,0:18:32.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大…大哥哥 我已经忍不住了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.52,0:18:34.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 就这么尿吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.36,0:18:36.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.50,0:18:38.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大哥哥会原谅你的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.64,0:18:58.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,日
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.07,0:19:03.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走到哪里才是个头啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.13,0:19:35.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哇 好多
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.66,0:19:38.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,话虽如此 但现在也不能逃了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.96,0:19:42.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,突击！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.75,0:19:51.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真…真是有够乱来啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.43,0:19:59.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿孝 快点
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.34,0:20:00.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别强人所难了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.51,0:20:04.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,平野 争取时间
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.53,0:20:05.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Jawohl！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.53,0:20:05.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7\fs24}注：德语 Yes的意思
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.01,0:20:17.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Gotcha！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.97,0:20:34.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小室君
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.47,0:20:36.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,孝
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.24,0:20:37.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小室
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.14,0:20:39.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大哥哥的朋友？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.88,0:20:43.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 重要的朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.79,0:20:48.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去往河对岸的末班车
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.28,0:20:50.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要上吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.20,0:20:52.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自然！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.20,0:20:57.97,title,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,0)\pos(407,307)\bord0\shad0}屍亂夜與屍群
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.06,0:22:34.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,重要救援人物 确保
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.86,0:22:35.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老师
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.84,0:22:36.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的好的～
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.27,0:22:46.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对…对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.31,0:22:57.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就这样 我们逃了出来
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.97,0:23:01.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当然…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.77,0:23:04.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这只不过是如同恶梦般的每日
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.36,0:23:08.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仅仅过去了一天而已
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.83,0:23:18.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而我们必须设法过河 与家人相会
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.79,0:23:32.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7\fs26}划啊划啊划啊划 划着小船
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.88,0:23:28.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呃 这孩子叫…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.20,0:23:28.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,希里爱丽丝
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.94,0:23:30.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an9\fs26}我们到黎明后都还没遇到<丧尸>
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.83,0:23:31.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an9\fs26}打不中
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.70,0:23:32.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小室 我来撑一会
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.51,0:23:32.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an9\fs26}谁会让你死啊
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.22,0:23:36.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是在突尼斯吗
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.10,0:23:41.02,title,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,0)\pos(406,307)\bord0\shad0}屍滿歸途
